{"tid":771612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次真係俾人睇蝕哂喇！北京戒嚴了？公安地鐵站堵路 拿民眾手機檢查訊息","createTime":"2018-08-08T05:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T08:59:08.000Z","uid":58552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3bb43f2e6f1914f6863b4df8da073227c2253d","tid":771612,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"（即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國網友在推特中瘋傳1段影片，指出在北京市地鐵西站內竟出現公安堵住通往月台的道路，要求民眾拿出手機解鎖並讓官方檢查通訊App裡的訊息內容，驚人影片曝光令網友直呼「要戒嚴了？」。<br />\n<br />\n從影片中能見到，6名公安在地鐵站內堵住通行民眾，3名公安負責維護現場秩序，另有3名公安要求民眾把手機螢幕鎖打開，並出示通訊App以供查驗訊息內容；網路上甚至出現「省廳指揮中心」8月1日發布的通知書，提及近期內因許多P2P網貸受害人進京抗議，因此要擴大查緝人民行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2512143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2512143&d=kWEa5PT6XUkPR0tRwgS8SPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=0b0cd0cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2512143&h=0cb00065\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2512143</a><br />\n<br />\n如果係edc有嚟，佢應該好撚淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d18f4af3946e5629fccf700fd0cbe310af12762","tid":771612,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"使撚咩,搵騰訊咪得囉"},{"pid":"8c440866dbadb369f2a4b6037b7769b0e5923b04","tid":771612,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"唔係用bot scan訊息既咩<br />\n<br />\n人手睇條撚咩？"},{"pid":"a5f283a7f375c6fb73144e9465e3fddcc17e0232","tid":771612,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4206aa0fd45bd273b5763d2bdc58c6d6d68f15b3","tid":771612,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c440866dbadb369f2a4b6037b7769b0e592